title: Federation University Players
body:
Anyone going to **Federation University** in Ballarat that plays League? Moving away from home and looking for some people to play with!
I've only been playing for a year and I play for fun, at mid silver at the moment.
Add me on League if you're interested in playing!


_JWhizz._




edit - not actually looking to play in the Oceanic University Championship, I'm garbage {{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
